  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight for your life in a fog-drenched world where evolved zombies hunt relentlessly.</strong> This uncompromising survival experience throws you into a post-apocalyptic nightmare where every shadow hides a threat and every resource matters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432420/extras/983f3d0cc641e3f27b094d33d9f1fdc7.poster.avif?t=1770901260\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432420/extras/983f3d0cc641e3f27b094d33d9f1fdc7.webm?t=1770901260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432420/extras/983f3d0cc641e3f27b094d33d9f1fdc7.mp4?t=1770901260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The dangers grow deadlier as you venture deeper into territories no survivor has conquered.</strong> Will you become the hunter, or remain the hunted in the deadly stillness of Silent Woods?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432420/extras/1205038bbfa902139130ae1918523a07.poster.avif?t=1770901260\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432420/extras/1205038bbfa902139130ae1918523a07.webm?t=1770901260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432420/extras/1205038bbfa902139130ae1918523a07.mp4?t=1770901260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A top-down action shooter set in a post-apocalyptic world shrouded in dense, unnatural fog.</strong> Deep in a remote forest crawling with twisted creatures and lurking dangers, you must survive using improvised technology, strange artifacts, and a flexible crafting system that rewards both strategy and adaptation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432420/extras/3a1c2c8e169681e817a1357067dcf677.poster.avif?t=1770901260\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432420/extras/3a1c2c8e169681e817a1357067dcf677.webm?t=1770901260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432420/extras/3a1c2c8e169681e817a1357067dcf677.mp4?t=1770901260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Armed with combat drones, spherical support robots, and alchemical workstations</strong>, you'll face off against an evolving threat of mutated undead and corrupted monstrosities. Supplies are limited—choosing the right upgrades and managing your resources wisely is key to staying alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beyond the survival gameplay, <strong>Silent Woods features a Story Mode</strong> that takes you through abandoned labs and forgotten facilities where puzzles and hidden lore slowly unveil the origins of this nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by classic horror atmospheres but driven by fast-paced, tactical gameplay, Silent Woods delivers a tense, ever-changing experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is only the beginning</strong>—new mechanics, enemies, and areas will be added regularly as the game evolves in Early Access.  </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight for your life in a fog-drenched world where evolved zombies hunt relentlessly.</strong> This uncompromising survival experience throws you into a post-apocalyptic nightmare where every shadow hides a threat and every resource matters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432420/extras/983f3d0cc641e3f27b094d33d9f1fdc7.poster.avif?t=1770901260\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432420/extras/983f3d0cc641e3f27b094d33d9f1fdc7.webm?t=1770901260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432420/extras/983f3d0cc641e3f27b094d33d9f1fdc7.mp4?t=1770901260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The dangers grow deadlier as you venture deeper into territories no survivor has conquered.</strong> Will you become the hunter, or remain the hunted in the deadly stillness of Silent Woods?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432420/extras/1205038bbfa902139130ae1918523a07.poster.avif?t=1770901260\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432420/extras/1205038bbfa902139130ae1918523a07.webm?t=1770901260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432420/extras/1205038bbfa902139130ae1918523a07.mp4?t=1770901260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A top-down action shooter set in a post-apocalyptic world shrouded in dense, unnatural fog.</strong> Deep in a remote forest crawling with twisted creatures and lurking dangers, you must survive using improvised technology, strange artifacts, and a flexible crafting system that rewards both strategy and adaptation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432420/extras/3a1c2c8e169681e817a1357067dcf677.poster.avif?t=1770901260\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432420/extras/3a1c2c8e169681e817a1357067dcf677.webm?t=1770901260\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432420/extras/3a1c2c8e169681e817a1357067dcf677.mp4?t=1770901260\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Armed with combat drones, spherical support robots, and alchemical workstations</strong>, you'll face off against an evolving threat of mutated undead and corrupted monstrosities. Supplies are limited—choosing the right upgrades and managing your resources wisely is key to staying alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beyond the survival gameplay, <strong>Silent Woods features a Story Mode</strong> that takes you through abandoned labs and forgotten facilities where puzzles and hidden lore slowly unveil the origins of this nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by classic horror atmospheres but driven by fast-paced, tactical gameplay, Silent Woods delivers a tense, ever-changing experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is only the beginning</strong>—new mechanics, enemies, and areas will be added regularly as the game evolves in Early Access.  </p>",
